node.text:
Look at this beauty 😍🦚 Peacock in a courtship display! 

📽 @l.fernandes24

The ornate train is believed to be the result of sexual selection by the females. Males use their ornate trains in a courtship display: they raise the feathers into a fan and quiver them.

node.text:
What is the relationship between architecture and @nature? 😍 Which photo is your favorite, from 1 to 10?

Save this post If you're planning to explore Iran for the most spectacular spots to visit! 📝

𝟭𝟬 𝗕𝗲𝗮𝘂𝘁𝗶𝗳𝘂𝗹 𝗔𝗿𝗰𝗵𝗶𝘁𝗲𝗰𝘁𝘂𝗿𝗮𝗹 𝗠𝗮𝗿𝘃𝗲𝗹𝘀 𝗶𝗻 𝗜𝗿𝗮𝗻
1. Imam Reza Holy Shrine
2. Nasir al Molk Mosque
3. Mollabashi Historical House
4. Hazrat Masumeh Holy Shrine
5. Nasir al Molk Mosque
6. National Arts Museum, Tehran
7. Shah Mosque
8. Sadoughi House Yazd
9. Jameh Mosque of Shafei
10. Borujerdiha Historical House

📸 @amir.hossein.mirmoeini
📍 Iran

Umbrella tree 🌳 How impressive is this holm oak? Known as the umbrella tree. Once a year two gardeners climb up into its crown on ladders, and for two weeks they prune the tree like a skirt as they meticulously trim it into shape. Its healing powers helped James Bond recuperate – Casino Royale.

📽 @brigrc
📍Villa del Balbianello, Como, Italy
